<p class="text-align-center"><strong>NOTICE OF SUPPLEMENTAL BUDGET HEARING</strong></p>
<p class="text-align-center">Use for Supplemental budget proposing an increase in a fund of 10% or more.</p>
<p class="text-align-center">A public hearing on a proposed supplemental budget for North Powder School District 8J, Union County, State of Oregon, for the fiscal year July 1, 2019 to June 30, 2020 will be held on the 28th day of April 2020 at 7:00 pm.<br>
The purpose of the hearing is to discus the supplemental budget. The regular Board Meeting will start at 6:00 pm.<strong> </strong></p>
<p class="text-align-center"><strong>View the entire notice: <a class="file file--mime-application-pdf file--application-pdf" data-entity-type="file" data-entity-uuid="30e1b9ef-2e6a-4e1a-bcb7-5c279e5fbea6" href="/sites/npowder.k12.or.us/files/inline-files/NP%20BUDGET%20NOTICE.pdf" rel="nofollow">PUBLIC NOTICE</a></strong></p>
<p class="text-align-center">In response to the current health emergency resulting from the COVID-19 pandemic the District facilities are currently closed to the public and meetings are being held by video conference only. This hearing will be available for public viewing via Zoom.<br>
The link to the meeting is: <a href="https://linkprotect.cudasvc.com/url?a=https%3a%2f%2fwww.google.com%2furl%3fq%3dhttps%253A%252F%252Fus02web.zoom.us%252Fj%252F85784939882%253Fpwd%253DR0RuU21JVzBQdjdmcXpCZTUrMlhFdz09%26sa%3dD%26ust%3d1588013734016000%26usg%3dAFQjCNE_5rH3S8AfmbO3A_wekOeyiQrMeg&amp;c=E,1,D6gzsR7KCiLXQcOcBTI52XqzPKCLcID1BnelPeiY64XUTlxfLeKIY1CFA5ejGFSTPik7kDBuHUxwpCJ0HLFXRhqHsyVaIICZCtkXsm8flfSt9EZKV7aGG5Mz&amp;typo=1" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">https://us02web.zoom.us/j/85784939882?pwd=R0RuU21JVzBQdjdmcXpCZTUrMlhFdz09</a></p>
